        <item>
            <title>1.13.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>A design refresh — new type, a new mark, and Liquid Glass.</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>New typography</b> — Alice for headings, Bitter for body text (Notes stay in a clean sans)</li>
                    <li><b>A new star mark</b> — the finished peach star on the home and app icon, in white elsewhere</li>
                    <li><b>Liquid Glass home</b> — the home cards are now real glass, with the starfield drifting behind them</li>
                    <li><b>A simpler home</b> — the Today view is gone; the home is one clean surface</li>
                    <li><b>Photo backgrounds fixed</b> — custom photo (and starfield) home backgrounds render correctly again</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
